<sect1 id="Second">
  <title>Second</title>

  <para><emphasis role="bold">STD.Date.Second<indexterm>
      <primary>STD.Date.Second</primary>
    </indexterm><indexterm>
      <primary>Date.Second</primary>
    </indexterm><indexterm>
      <primary>Second</primary>
    </indexterm>(</emphasis> <emphasis>time</emphasis> <emphasis
  role="bold">)</emphasis></para>

  <informaltable colsep="1" frame="all" rowsep="1">
    <tgroup cols="2">
      <colspec colwidth="80.50pt"/>

      <colspec/>

      <tbody>
        <row>
          <entry><emphasis>time</emphasis></entry>

          <entry>Um valor de hora no formato Time_.</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry>Return:</entry>

          <entry>Second retorna um valor INTEGER que representa os segundos no
          intervalo de 0 a 59.</entry>
        </row>
      </tbody>
    </tgroup>
  </informaltable>

  <para>A função <emphasis role="bold">Second </emphasis> retorna os segundos
  do valor de <emphasis>time</emphasis> .</para>

  <para>Exemplo:</para>

  <programlisting format="linespecific">IMPORT STD;
MyTime:= STD.Date.CurrentTime(TRUE);   //Local Time
  
t1 := STD.Date.Second(MyTime);
    //t1 contains the second of the current local time
</programlisting>

  <para/>
</sect1>
